        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
                <div class="testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
                <p class="testimonial-text">"Modern design, great quality, and affordable prices. FurniStyle is now my go-to for all furniture needs. Highly recommended!"</p>
                <div class="testimonial-author">
                    <div class="author-avatar">MR</div>
                    <div class="author-info">
                        <div class="author-name">Maria Reyes</div>
                        <div class="author-location">Makati, Philippines</div>
                    </div>
